<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<section class="page-header" style="padding-bottom:60px;">
  <span class="eyebrow">Process</span>
  <h1 class="display">One disciplined path,<br>every engagement.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Whether it&rsquo;s a rebrand, AI search visibility, or a custom automation build, we run the same five steps &mdash; then keep iterating so results compound instead of stalling.</p>
</section>

<section class="container" style="padding:20px 24px 90px;">
  <div class="step-list">
    <div class="step-row">
      <span class="step-row__num">01</span>
      <div class="step-row__body">
        <h2>Audit</h2>
        <p>We start by understanding your brand, your goals, and where you stand today &mdash; from how you show up to where you&rsquo;re invisible or losing time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-row">
      <span class="step-row__num">02</span>
      <div class="step-row__body">
        <h2>Strategy</h2>
        <p>We map the plan: what to fix first, what to build, and the fastest path to a result you can measure &mdash; prioritized around your goals, not a generic checklist.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-row">
      <span class="step-row__num">03</span>
      <div class="step-row__body">
        <h2>Build</h2>
        <p>We do the work &mdash; branding, content, schema, automations, integrations &mdash; not just advise. You get finished deliverables, not a slide deck of recommendations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-row">
      <span class="step-row__num">04</span>
      <div class="step-row__body">
        <h2>Launch &amp; grow</h2>
        <p>We ship it into the world and push for traction across every channel that matters &mdash; search, AI answer engines, and the places your buyers actually are.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-row">
      <span class="step-row__num">05</span>
      <div class="step-row__body">
        <h2>Measure &amp; iterate</h2>
        <p>Real numbers, clear reporting, and continuous improvement. We track what&rsquo;s working, cut what isn&rsquo;t, and feed every learning back into step one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band section--top-border">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <h2>Let&rsquo;s get started.</h2>
    <p>Book a strategy call and we&rsquo;ll begin with a clear-eyed audit of where you stand.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book a strategy call</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
